rows.name: question_1
rows.value: What was your role in the session

rows.name: question_3
rows.value: How long did the session last?

rows.name: question_4
rows.value: How much time did you spend on preparing for the session?

rows.name: question_5
rows.value: Were you able to complete all the activities?

rows.name: question_6
rows.value: What activities were you not able to complete? Why?

rows.name: confidence_header
rows.value: How confident are you in the following?

rows.name: question_7
rows.value: On your knowledge about Talking about Feelings

rows.name: question_8
rows.value: On your facilitation skills for Talking about Feelings

rows.name: question_9
rows.value: What challenges did you face in delivering the module that you would like to discuss in the coaching session? Be specific.

rows.name: question_10
rows.value: What is your goal or what do you want to achieve or learn from the coaching session?

rows.name: question_11
rows.value: Which of the parents in this group attended your in-person session?
